$ RMAN: backup retention policy
@ backup retention policy

The *backup retention policy* defines how long → development/databases/Oracle/adminstration/backup-recovery/backup[backups] and → development/databases/Oracle/architecture/database/files/archived-redo-log[archived logs] must be retained for → development/databases/Oracle/adminstration/backup-recovery/recovery/media.

A retention policy is defined in terms of
  • backup redundancy or
  • a → development/databases/Oracle/adminstration/backup-recovery/backup/retention-policy/recovery-window

